能說你係強逆命運。<br />\n再加上有錢人去私家醫院仲有得打尖呢下睇得岀移植器官根本係個唔唔公平嘅機制。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1565e6b3ef136687f1b4b954a352fcc80db4c831","tid":1701264,"uid":230707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T05:37:28.000Z","msg":"呢一刻，棄官緊要啲...."},{"pid":"5551cc9eb60dccfc477eba3d81e2de4a51aee30d","tid":1701264,"uid":9315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T05:42:01.000Z","msg":"公開下政府官員有幾多登記左先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係咪自己等器官用渣<br />\n<br />\n叫人搭高鐵自己就搭飛機<br />\n叫人投資大灣區自己就買英美樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56da802da11b17d2d25f611219b6f90ef579c064","tid":1701264,"uid":24443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T05:46:09.000Z","msg":"佢意思係幫的高官填呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}